        com.esotericsoftware.kryo.Kryo get()
        Provide a Kryo instance unique to the calling thread. This method must return distinct instances when called from distinct threads. This method may return distinct instances when called at various times from a single thread, or it may cache an instance and return it to a single thread on every call.
        Returns:
        a Kryo instance
